data.description: Come take a look at this spacious 4 bedroom/ 2 and a half  bath home. This property offers a 2 car garage and sits on almost half an acre. With an extra room, this space could be used as an office, sitting room, play room, reading room, what fits the imagination for the next home owner! Located in the heart of Waco; Easy convenience for groceries, shopping, food, etc. Dishwasher and Dryer and negotiable. Appliances convey with property. Can't show up in person, no problem! We have virtual tour as well!
